2011-04-27  Thien-Thi Nguyen  <ttn@gnuvola.org>

	[int] Add abstraction: LOOKUP

	Suggested by Brian Templeton.

	* guile-sdl.h (LOOKUP): New macro.
	* sdlenums.c (gsdl_init_enums): Use it.

